<paragraph blockId="13.[160,1155,697,827]" pageId="13" pageNumber="2851">The ZSI collection has one glass bottle for this species labelled as ‘holotype’ (5045/18) containing a female specimen in poor condition. The same bottle has a small glass vial containing the dissected epigyne.</paragraph>
